column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, f.z as photoz, f.zErr as photoZerr, GN.distance, s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift, s.zErr as errredshift, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#., #, #) AS GN on p.objid = GN.objid join Photoz as f ON f.objid = GN.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = GN.objid
